<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<div class="row justify-content-center my-5">
  <div class="col-lg-8">
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg rounded-4 p-5 bg-white">
      <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-danger me-2"></i>Privacy Policy
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted small">Last Updated: May 23, 2026</p>
      <hr class="my-4">
      
      <div class="text-secondary" style="line-height: 1.7;">
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark">1. Information We Collect</h5>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us when registering an account, creating or updating a property listing, making bookings, or communicating with us. This includes your name, email address, password, phone number, and listing details.</p>
        
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h5>
        <p>We use the information we collect to operate, maintain, and improve our hotel booking services, process payments and bookings, communicate transaction confirmations, and offer a personalized search experience.</p>
        
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mt-4">3. Security and Storage</h5>
        <p>We implement a variety of industry-standard security measures to safeguard your personal data. Stored user details, bookings, and passwords are encrypted and protected behind authentication layers.</p>
        
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mt-4">4. Sharing of Information</h5>
        <p>We do not share, sell, or rent your personal information to third parties, except as necessary to complete bookings, verify payments (e.g. via UPI/Razorpay), or comply with regulatory authorities.</p>
        
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mt-4">5. Contact Us</h5>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@wonderfull.com" class="text-danger">support@wonderfull.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-top text-center">
        <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-danger rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold shadow-sm">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-1"></i>Back to Explore
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
